#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&trojita; is an email program (\"client\") focused on IMAP email accounts, "
"where the mail remains on the server but is manipulated by the software you "
"run on the computer under your fingertips. It is designed to be simple (it "
"can be built using only one single dependent library), and fast and "
"efficient over the network, economizing resources and limiting data "
"transfer. Its GUI is intended to be uncluttered and efficient, and it "
"provides \"expensive mode\" data transfer, that reduces the length of its "
"conversation with the server to a minimum. It is a stand-alone program, not "
"part of a bigger or more complex suite. As it is under development, some "
"features are still missing."
msgstr ""
"&trojita; je e-poštni program (\"odjemalec\"), osredotočen na e-poštne "
"račune IMAP, kjer pošta ostane na strežniku, vendar jo upravlja programska "
"oprema, ki jo izvajate v računalniku pod vašimi prsti. Zasnovan je tako, da "
"je preprost (lahko ga zgradite z uporabo samo ene same odvisne knjižnice) "
"ter hiter in učinkovit prek omrežja, varčuje z viri in omejuje prenos "
"podatkov. Njegov GUI naj bi bil preprost in učinkovit ter zagotavlja prenos "
"podatkov v \"dragem načinu\", ki skrajša dolžino njegovega pogovora s "
"strežnikom na minimum. Je samostojen program, ki ni del večje ali bolj "
"zapletene zbirke. Ker je v razvoju, nekatere funkcije še vedno manjkajo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &trojita;"
msgstr "Uporaba &trojita;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&trojita; allows you to read, write, organize, search for, and send email. "
"If you've got an IMAP email account, &trojita; will allow you to access and "
"use it. IMAP is a protocol that allows your mail to stay on the server, "
"rather than downloading it to your local machine. However, &trojita; does in "
"fact download parts of your messages &ndash; even all of your messages "
"&ndash; for convenience. In the 1990s, most people used POP3 mailboxes, and "
"their email software downloaded all their messages, removing them from the "
"server. The disadvantage was that if you used any other computer, your "
"messages were not available. IMAP solves that problem by keeping the mail on "
"the server. The software you use on your local computer/cellphone simply "
"issues instructions (\"reply to this email,\" \"display this email,\" &etc;) "
"for the server to execute."
msgstr ""
"&trojita; omogoča branje, pisanje, organiziranje, iskanje in pošiljanje e-"
"pošte. Če imate e-poštni račun IMAP, &trojita; vam bo omogočil dostop in "
"uporabo. IMAP je protokol, ki omogoča, da vaša pošta ostane na strežniku, "
"namesto da bi jo prenašali na vaš lokalni računalnik. Vendar &trojita; "
"dejansko prenese dele vaših sporočil &ndash; celo vsa vaša sporočila &ndash; "
"za udobje. V devetdesetih letih je večina ljudi uporabljala nabiralnike POP3 "
"in njihova e-poštna programska oprema je prenesla vsa njihova sporočila in "
"jih odstranila s strežnika. Pomanjkljivost je bila, da vaša sporočila niso "
"bila na voljo, če ste uporabljali kateri koli drug računalnik. IMAP rešuje "
"to težavo tako, da obdrži pošto na strežniku. Programska oprema, ki jo "
"uporabljate na lokalnem računalniku/mobilnem telefonu, preprosto izda "
"navodila (»odgovori na to e-pošto«, »prikaži to e-pošto« &etc;), ki naj jih "
"strežnik izvede."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First you need an IMAP account. There are many providers; <ulink url="
"\"http://fastmail.fm\">FastMail</ulink> is one; <ulink url=\"http://tuffmail."
"com\">Tuffmail</ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://pobox.com\">Pobox</ulink> are "
"others. Google's Gmail service provides IMAP access to your Gmail account "
"(Outlook and others do not). And if the manager of your &Microsoft; "
"<application>Exchange</application> server has configured it, you can access "
"<application>Exchange</application> through IMAP as well. If you have got an "
"IMAP account, a user name and password, that is all you should need to use "
"&trojita; to access it."
msgstr ""
"Najprej potrebujete račun IMAP. Ponudnikov je veliko; <ulink url=\"http://"
"fastmail.fm\">FastMail</ulink> je eden; <ulink url=\"http://tuffmail.com"
"\">Tuffmail</ulink> in <ulink url=\"http://pobox.com\">Pobox</ulink> sta "
"druga. Googlova storitev Gmail omogoča dostop IMAP do vašega računa Gmail "
"(Outlook in drugi ne). In če upravitelj vašega &Microsoft; Strežnik "
"<application>Exchange</application> ga je konfiguriral, do "
"<application>Exchange</application> lahko dostopate tudi prek IMAP. Če imate "
"račun IMAP, uporabniško ime in geslo, je to vse, kar potrebujete za uporabo "
"&trojita; za dostop do njega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that not all IMAP providers are equal and some offer service that is "
"frustratingly slow. &Microsoft;'s <application>Exchange</application> server "
"too is reported to be somewhat slow. If you choose a good provider and use "
"fast software, you'll be surprised how pleasant an experience it can be."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da niso vsi ponudniki IMAP enaki in nekateri ponujajo storitev, "
"ki je frustrirajoče počasna. Tudi &Microsoft;ov strežnik "
"<application>Exchange</application> naj bi bil nekoliko počasen. Če izberete "
"dobrega ponudnika in uporabljate hitro programsko opremo, boste presenečeni, "
"kako prijetna izkušnja je lahko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring your IMAP Account"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje vašega računa IMAP"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, click on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab of the Settings box. "
"Add your IMAP account as a new account, using these parameters:"
msgstr ""
"Najprej kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> v polju z "
"nastavitvami. Dodajte svoj račun IMAP kot nov račun z uporabo teh parametrov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Real Name: the name you want to show on your emails (your own first and last "
"name)"
msgstr ""
"Pravo ime: ime, ki ga želite prikazati v svojih e-poštnih sporočilih (vaše "
"ime in priimek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email: your email address"
msgstr "E-pošta: vaš e-poštni naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organisation: your company name (optional)"
msgstr "Organizacija: ime vašega podjetja (neobvezno)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Signature: any text you want to appear at the bottom of your emails, like "
"your website name or a slogan"
msgstr ""
"Podpis: poljubno besedilo, ki ga želite prikazati na dnu vaših e-poštnih "
"sporočil, na primer ime vašega spletnega mesta ali slogan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These settings become an identity, and you can have several, if you want, if "
"for example, some of your mail is part of a mailing list where your messages "
"should look different (a different signature line, for example). Note "
"however that at present, &trojita; does not yet permit multiple IMAP "
"accounts (that is, use with multiple servers)."
msgstr ""
"Te nastavitve postanejo identiteta in imate jih lahko več, če želite, če je "
"na primer nekaj vaše pošte del poštnega seznama, kjer bi morala biti vaša "
"sporočila videti drugače (na primer druga vrstica za podpis). Upoštevajte "
"pa, da trenutno &trojita; še ne dovoljuje več računov IMAP (to je uporabe z "
"več strežniki)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next, add the connection parameters necessary to access your account."
msgstr "Nato dodajte parametre povezave, potrebne za dostop do vašega računa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Method: choose SSL, if your provider requires it. Otherwise, choose \"TCP\" "
"for a connection that starts unencrypted and may be upgraded to encryption "
"while connecting. And if your provider requires you to perform that upgrade "
"to encryption, check the \"perform STARTTLS command\" to ensure it does. "
"\"Local process\" is for advanced users who, for example, are connecting to "
"their provider over another SSH agent (in this case you'd put something like "
"<userinput>ssh imap.provider.org dovecot --exec-mail imap</userinput>). "
"Generally, TCP or SSL are your two most likely choices."
msgstr ""
"Metoda: izberite SSL, če ga vaš ponudnik zahteva. V nasprotnem primeru "
"izberite »TCP« za povezavo, ki se začne nešifrirano in se lahko med "
"povezovanjem nadgradi na šifriranje. In če vaš ponudnik zahteva, da izvedete "
"to nadgradnjo na šifriranje, preverite \"izvedi ukaz STARTTLS\", da "
"zagotovite, da to stori. »Lokalni postopek« je za napredne uporabnike, ki se "
"na primer povezujejo s svojim ponudnikom prek drugega agenta SSH (v tem "
"primeru bi vstavili nekaj takega kot <userinput>ssh imap.provider.org "
"dovecot --exec-mail imap</userinput>). Na splošno sta dve najverjetnejši "
"izbiri TCP ali SSL."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "IMAP Server: is your provider's server (&eg; mail.host.com)"
msgstr "Strežnik IMAP: je strežnik vašega ponudnika (&eg; mail.host.com)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Port: this parameter should change automatically depending on what you enter "
"for \"IMAP Server.\" Typically it is 143 for unencrypted connections and 993 "
"for SSL connections."
msgstr ""
"Vrata: ta parameter bi se moral samodejno spremeniti glede na to, kaj "
"vnesete za »Strežnik IMAP«. Običajno je 143 za nešifrirane povezave in 993 "
"za povezave SSL."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Username: your username"
msgstr "Uporabniško ime: vaše uporabniško ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Password: your password. At present, &trojita; stores your user name and "
"password in a plain text file on your computer. This is not secure! If that "
"worries you, leave the password field blank, and &trojita; will ask you once "
"for your password, and keep it in memory until the application exits."
msgstr ""
"Geslo: vaše geslo. Trenutno &trojita; shrani vaše uporabniško ime in geslo v "
"datoteko z navadnim besedilom na vašem računalniku. To ni varno! Če vas to "
"skrbi, pustite polje za geslo prazno in &trojita; vas bo enkrat vprašala za "
"geslo in ga hranila v pomnilniku, dokler aplikacija ne zapre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start in Offline Mode:"
msgstr "Začnite v načinu brez povezave:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Blacklisted Capabilities: &trojita; strives to be standards compliant. But "
"some servers that advertise standards compliance are not actually so. If "
"you're aware of some features that your provider advertises but does not "
"actually provide, listing them here allows &trojita; to politely ignore them."
msgstr ""
"Zmogljivosti na črnem seznamu: &trojita; si prizadeva biti skladen s "
"standardi. Toda nekateri strežniki, ki oglašujejo skladnost s standardi, "
"dejansko niso takšni. Če ste seznanjeni z nekaterimi funkcijami, ki jih vaš "
"ponudnik oglašuje, vendar jih v resnici ne zagotavlja, jih navedete tukaj in "
"&trojita; da jih vljudno ignorira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Offline</guilabel> mode tab is where you configure &trojita;'s "
"ability to store local copies of messages on your server. The advantage of "
"saving a copy locally is obvious: you can access it later without "
"reconnecting. The disadvantages include filling up your local hard disk, and "
"of course the security risk if anyone ever goes exploring on your computer. "
"&trojita;'s default is to store local copies indefinitely, but here you may "
"choose if you prefer to store up to a certain number of days, or to not "
"store at all. Note that the code to clean the message cache has not yet been "
"implemented, so at present you should assume the message cache will not be "
"pruned."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek načina <guilabel>Brez povezave</guilabel> je kraj, kjer "
"konfigurirate sposobnost &trojita; za shranjevanje lokalnih kopij sporočil "
"na vaš strežnik. Prednost lokalnega shranjevanja kopije je očitna: do nje "
"lahko dostopate pozneje brez ponovne povezave. Slabosti vključujejo "
"polnjenje vašega lokalnega trdega diska in seveda varnostno tveganje, če kdo "
"kdaj začne raziskovati vaš računalnik. &trojita; privzeto shranjuje lokalne "
"kopije za nedoločen čas, tukaj pa lahko izberete, ali želite shraniti do "
"določenega števila dni ali jih sploh ne želite. Upoštevajte, da koda za "
"čiščenje predpomnilnika sporočil še ni bila implementirana, zato trenutno "
"predvidevajte, da predpomnilnik sporočil ne bo odstranjen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>SMTP</guilabel> tab is where you configure sending email."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>SMTP</guilabel> je kraj, kjer konfigurirate pošiljanje e-"
"pošte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Method: choose SMTP for unencrypted connections, or \"secure SMTP\" if you "
"prefer (and your provider accepts) mail sent over SSL. If you choose \"local "
"sendmail-compatible\" &trojita; will simply pass your mail to the sendmail "
"app running on your local computer (and if you haven't got one, it will "
"fail). Choosing this option requires you specify the sendmail parameters for "
"using your local sendmail."
msgstr ""
"Metoda: izberite SMTP za nešifrirane povezave ali \"varen SMTP\", če vam je "
"ljubša (in vaš ponudnik to sprejema) pošta poslana prek SSL. Če izberete "
"\"združljivo z lokalnim sendmailom\" &trojita; bo vašo pošto preprosto "
"posredoval aplikaciji sendmail, ki se izvaja v vašem lokalnem računalniku "
"(in če je nimate, ne bo delovala). Če izberete to možnost, morate določiti "
"parametre sendmail za uporabo lokalnega sendmaila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "SMTP server: the name of the server to which your mail should be sent."
msgstr "Strežnik SMTP: ime strežnika, na katerega naj se pošlje vaša pošta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Port: This parameter should change automatically depending on what you "
"choose for \"Method.\" Typically, it's 587 for unencrypted mail, and 465 for "
"mail sent over SSL."
msgstr ""
"Vrata: Ta parameter bi se moral samodejno spremeniti glede na to, kaj "
"izberete za »Metodo«. Običajno je 587 za nešifrirano pošto in 465 za pošto, "
"poslano prek SSL."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sendmail Executable: is only required if you've chosen \"local sendmail-"
"compatible\" as your method. If so, here you should put whatever command is "
"required for your message to be sent to your local sendmail app. The default "
"is \"sendmail -bm -oi\" but if your local configuration is non-standard, "
"you'll have to adjust this parameter appropriately."
msgstr ""
"Izvedljiva datoteka Sendmail: potrebna je le, če ste kot metodo izbrali "
"\"združljivo z lokalnim sendmailom\". Če je tako, bi morali tukaj vnesti "
"kateri koli ukaz, ki je potreben, da bo vaše sporočilo poslano v vašo "
"lokalno aplikacijo sendmail. Privzeto je \"sendmail -bm -oi\", vendar če "
"vaša lokalna konfiguracija ni standardna, boste morali ta parameter ustrezno "
"prilagoditi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"StartTLS: check this box if your provider requires a TLS connection to send "
"encrypted mail (this is not the same as using SSL by choosing \"Secure SMTP"
"\" as your method above)."
msgstr ""
"StartTLS: potrdite to polje, če vaš ponudnik zahteva povezavo TLS za "
"pošiljanje šifrirane pošte (to ni isto kot uporaba SSL, če kot zgornji način "
"izberete »Varen SMTP«)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"SMTP Auth: if you must input a user name and password in order to send mail, "
"check this box. In the modern age, you almost always have to do so, as "
"otherwise spammers send unwanted messages through the server."
msgstr ""
"SMTP Auth: če morate za pošiljanje pošte vnesti uporabniško ime in geslo, "
"potrdite to polje. V moderni dobi je to skoraj vedno treba storiti, sicer "
"pošiljatelji neželene pošte prek strežnika pošiljajo neželena sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Username: your user name."
msgstr "Uporabniško ime: vaše uporabniško ime."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your password."
msgstr "Vaše geslo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save outgoing mail: if you check this box, &trojita; will save a copy of "
"every mail you send. This has been the default setting for all email "
"programs for so long now that few people even know it's possible to not do "
"so!"
msgstr ""
"Shrani odhodno pošto: če označite to polje, &trojita; bo shranil kopijo "
"vsake poslane pošte. To je že tako dolgo privzeta nastavitev za vse e-poštne "
"programe, da malokdo sploh ve, da tega ni mogoče storiti!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sent folder name: If you do decide to keep a local copy of your sent mail, "
"choose in which folder you'd like to keep it."
msgstr ""
"Ime poslane mape: Če se odločite obdržati lokalno kopijo poslane pošte, "
"izberite, v kateri mapi jo želite obdržati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send with BURL: The BURL extension is an extension to the IMAP standard, "
"implemented in 2006, so not all servers make the service available. Imagine "
"you have a huge email in your inbox with an attachment, and you'd like to "
"forward that message. The normal way requires your IMAP client to download "
"that huge message, and then resend it (causing two large network transfers). "
"The BURL extension allows you to send that message without having to "
"download it first. If your provider permits BURL, it's worth selecting this "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Pošlji z BURL: Razširitev BURL je razširitev standarda IMAP, uvedena leta "
"2006, zato storitev ni na voljo na vseh strežnikih. Predstavljajte si, da "
"imate v mapi »Prejeto« ogromno e-poštnega sporočila s priponko in bi to "
"sporočilo radi posredovali naprej. Običajen način zahteva, da vaš odjemalec "
"IMAP prenese to ogromno sporočilo in ga nato znova pošlje (kar povzroči dva "
"velika omrežna prenosa). Razširitev BURL vam omogoča pošiljanje tega "
"sporočila, ne da bi ga morali najprej prenesti. Če vaš ponudnik dovoljuje "
"BURL, je vredno izbrati to možnost."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reading Mail with &trojita;"
msgstr "Branje pošte s &trojita;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&trojita; presents a three paned interface that should be anyone who has "
"ever used email before. On the left side is a list of all your email "
"folders, probably INBOX and some others. On the right side are two panes: "
"the top pane shows the list of all messages in the current folder, and the "
"bottom pane shows the message selected in the top pane. &Microsoft; Outlook, "
"&kmail; and many other email clients all use this same layout."
msgstr ""
"&trojita; predstavlja vmesnik s tremi ploščami, ki bi moral biti vsak, ki je "
"že kdaj uporabljal e-pošto. Na levi strani je seznam vseh vaših e-poštnih "
"map, verjetno INBOX in nekaterih drugih. Na desni strani sta dve podokni: "
"zgornje podokno prikazuje seznam vseh sporočil v trenutni mapi, spodnje "
"podokno pa prikazuje sporočilo, izbrano v zgornjem podoknu. &Microsoft; "
"Outlook, &kmail; in mnogi drugi e-poštni odjemalci uporabljajo isto "
"postavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other layouts are available, however. Under the <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"menu, simply select <menuchoice><guimenu>Layout</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Wide</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to choose instead a three pane layout suitable for "
"larger, wider screens, where your folders are shown in the left column, the "
"messages of the selected folder in the center column, and the contents of "
"the selected message in the right column."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo pa so tudi druge postavitve. V meniju <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"preprosto izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavitev</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Široko</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da namesto tega izberete "
"postavitev s tremi podokni, primerno za večje, širše zaslone , kjer so vaše "
"mape prikazane v levem stolpcu, sporočila izbrane mape v srednjem stolpcu in "
"vsebina izbranega sporočila v desnem stolpcu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select a message, it will be displayed below. Right click on the "
"selected message in the top pane if you'd like to delete the message, save "
"it to disk as a text file, or view all the headers."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete sporočilo, bo prikazano spodaj. Desni klik na izbrano sporočilo "
"v zgornjem podoknu, če želite izbrisati sporočilo, ga shraniti na disk kot "
"besedilno datoteko ali si ogledati vse glave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To respond to, or forward a message, use the buttons on the toolbar, as no "
"keystroke shortcuts are currently defined. Choose <guibutton>Private Reply</"
"guibutton> to respond only to the sender. Choose <guibutton>Reply to All</"
"guibutton> if you'd like to reply to the sender and everyone else on the To: "
"or CC: lines. If the message arrived through a properly-configured mailing "
"list, the <guibutton>Reply to Mailing List</guibutton> option will also be "
"made available."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odgovoriti na sporočilo ali ga posredovati, uporabite gumbe v "
"orodni vrstici, saj trenutno ni definirana nobena bližnjica na tipki. "
"Izberite <guibutton>Zasebni odgovor</guibutton>, če želite odgovoriti samo "
"pošiljatelju. Izberite <guibutton>Odgovori vsem</guibutton>, če želite "
"odgovoriti pošiljatelju in vsem drugim v vrsticah Za: ali CC:. Če je "
"sporočilo prispelo prek pravilno konfiguriranega poštnega seznama, bo na "
"voljo tudi možnost <guibutton>Odgovori na poštni seznam</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "At present, the \"Forward message\" function has not yet been included."
msgstr "Trenutno funkcija \"Posreduj sporočilo\" še ni vključena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing/Composing Mail"
msgstr "Pisanje/sestavljanje pošte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To compose a new message, click the icon at the far left of the toolbar. A "
"new message window will appear, where you can choose your recipients, "
"compose your text, and send. If you get interrupted and need to save a "
"draft, you can do so by clicking on the little expander menu next to the "
"send button. A draft will then be saved in your drafts folder."
msgstr ""
"Če želite sestaviti novo sporočilo, kliknite ikono na skrajni levi strani "
"orodne vrstice. Pojavilo se bo novo okno za sporočilo, kjer lahko izberete "
"svoje prejemnike, sestavite besedilo in pošljete. Če vas motijo in morate "
"shraniti osnutek, lahko to storite tako, da kliknete majhen razširitveni "
"meni poleg gumba za pošiljanje. Osnutek bo nato shranjen v vaši mapi z "
"osnutki."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Address Book"
msgstr "Adresar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At present, &trojita; does not have a graphical addressbook, though one is "
"actively being developed. However, in the meantime, there's a very effective "
"work-around. Upon start up, &trojita; reads the address book located in "
"<filename role=\"directory\">~/.abook/</filename>, which you can create "
"using the console-only program called <application>abook</application>. "
"Running <application>abook</application> in a terminal window like "
"&konsole;, you can add, delete, and edit address book entries. &trojita; "
"doesn't manipulate that address book in any way, so for example, it won't "
"add new entries as you write messages. But if you've got an <filename role="
"\"extension\">.abook</filename> address book, &trojita; will auto-complete "
"entries using it."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno &trojita; nima grafičnega adresarja, čeprav se aktivno razvija. "
"Vendar pa v tem času obstaja zelo učinkovita rešitev. Ob zagonu &trojita; "
"bere adresar, ki se nahaja v <filename role=\"directory\">~/.abook/</"
"filename>, ki ga lahko ustvarite s programom samo za konzolo, imenovanim "
"<application>abook</application>. Če zaženete <application>abook</"
"application> v terminalskem oknu, kot je &konsole;, lahko dodajate, brišete "
"in urejate vnose v imeniku. &trojita; na noben način ne manipulira s tem "
"imenikom, tako da na primer ne bo dodajal novih vnosov, ko pišete sporočila. "
"Če pa imate imenik <filename role=\"extension\">.abook</filename>, &trojita; "
"bo z njo samodejno dokončal vnose."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &trojita; window"
msgstr "Glavna &trojita; okno"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "The IMAP Menu"
msgstr "Meni IMAP"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compose Mail...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sestavi sporočilo...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new message for editing"
msgstr "Odpre novo sporočilo za urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Expunge Mailbox</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>IMAP</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbriši nabiralnik</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes from the server any message already marked for deletion in the "
"currently selected mailbox (folder)."
msgstr ""
"Iz strežnika odstrani vsa sporočila, ki so že označena za brisanje v "
"trenutno izbranem nabiralniku (mapi)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Network Access</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Offline</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Dostop do omrežja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Brez povezave</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, &trojita; will not fetch any new data (messages) from your "
"server and will rather limit itself to the messages you have previously "
"downloaded. (It will still let you compose new messages, however, even "
"though you won't be able to send them)."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrano, &trojita; ne bo pridobil novih podatkov (sporočil) iz vašega "
"strežnika in se bo raje omejil na sporočila, ki ste jih predhodno prenesli. "
"(Vendar vam bo še vedno omogočal sestavljanje novih sporočil, čeprav jih ne "
"boste mogli poslati)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Network Access</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Expensive Connection</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Dostop do omrežja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Draga povezava</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this if you're using &trojita; on a cell-phone or other device where "
"it's important to reduce network traffic and be efficient."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite to, če uporabljate &trojita; na mobilnem telefonu ali drugi "
"napravi, kjer je pomembno zmanjšati omrežni promet in biti učinkovit."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Network Access</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Free Access</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Dostop do omrežja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prost dostop</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this if you are on a desktop computer with unlimited broadband internet "
"access. This permits &trojita; to more aggressively preload data. That is, "
"instead of just downloading headers, for example, it will go right ahead and "
"download a local copy of the messages, too."
msgstr ""
"To uporabite, če uporabljate namizni računalnik z neomejenim širokopasovnim "
"dostopom do interneta. To dovoljuje &trojita; za bolj agresivno "
"prednalaganje podatkov. To pomeni, da bo na primer namesto samo prenosa "
"glav, šel takoj naprej in prenesel tudi lokalno kopijo sporočil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Layout</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Postavitev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guimenuitem>Wide</guimenuitem> for a modern, three-panel view with "
"the message list in the center and the message itself on the right. Choose "
"<guimenuitem>Compact</guimenuitem> for the traditional three panel view with "
"the message list on top and the message itself on the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guimenuitem>Široko</guimenuitem> za sodoben pogled s tremi "
"ploščami s seznamom sporočil na sredini in samim sporočilom na desni. "
"Izberite <guimenuitem>Kompaktno</guimenuitem> za tradicionalni pogled treh "
"plošč s seznamom sporočil na vrhu in samim sporočilom na dnu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Messages in Threads</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži sporočila v nitih</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to show messages grouped into threads (conversations). "
"This is useful for mailing lists, for example. This depends on your IMAP "
"server supporting one or more voluntary extensions, as &trojita; would "
"otherwise have to do more work to properly thread messages."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite prikazati sporočila, združena v niti "
"(pogovore). To je na primer uporabno za poštne sezname. To je odvisno od "
"tega, ali vaš strežnik IMAP podpira eno ali več prostovoljnih razširitev, "
"kot je &trojita; bi sicer moral opraviti več dela, da bi pravilno povezoval "
"sporočila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hide Read Messages</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skrij prebrana sporočila</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose this option if you like only new messages to appear in the message "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite, da se na seznamu sporočil prikažejo samo "
"nova sporočila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Only Subscribed Folders</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži samo naročene mape</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your mailbox may have more folders than you actually need to monitor. Select "
"this option to limit the folders shown to only those you've subscribed to. "
"(This doesn't delete the other folders, it just prevents them from being "
"shown in the list of folders)."
msgstr ""
"Vaš nabiralnik ima morda več map, kot jih dejansko potrebujete. Izberite to "
"možnost, če želite omejiti prikazane mape samo na tiste, na katere ste "
"naročeni. (S tem ne izbrišete drugih map, le preprečite, da bi bile "
"prikazane na seznamu map)."

